Problem Statement

https://leetcode.com/problems/exchange-seats/


Problem Solution

SELECT
      CASE WHEN MOD(id, 2) = 0 THEN id - 1
           WHEN MOD(id, 2) != 0 AND id = cnt THEN id
           ELSE id + 1 END AS id,
           student
FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS cnt
       FROM Seat) AS cnt_table, Seat
ORDER BY id
